{"tid":1294134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方唔克制驅散示威者：認X住我呀！隻揪呀！","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:50:09.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07dbbf22d3437fc461745b43e66d262a38b20680","tid":1294134,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190708/large/1562517875_7557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190708%2Flarge%2F1562517875_7557.jpg&h=964a1637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方晚上於旺角彌敦道驅散示威者，其中有一條片段在telegram群組流傳，清楚見到有警員驅散示威者期間，一名年約20歲的男子絆倒在地上，在場示威人士不齒警方強硬驅散，於是破口大罵，但警員竟然沒有克制，大聲呼喝：「咩呀！」，之後雙方不斷推撞，有警員更指：「認X住我呀」「隻揪呀」，意圖令示威者的不滿情緒加劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190707/59799355?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR29tiByvexX5tSFd1z_4vl0OiuSxHV3QO2IwQhsr04hwRhUrb6IAzRs4WA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190707%2F59799355%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR29tiByvexX5tSFd1z_4vl0OiuSxHV3QO2IwQhsr04hwRhUrb6IAzRs4WA&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=bdba5f58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190707%2F59799355%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR29tiByvexX5tSFd1z_4vl0OiuSxHV3QO2IwQhsr04hwRhUrb6IAzRs4WA&h=3dce7138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190707/59799355?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&